{"ID":"20230817162003-103ubc2","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20230817162003-103ubc2","title":"Transformation和Action","updated":"20230817162003"},"Children":[{"ID":"20230817162004-1mev5ti","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20230817162004-1mev5ti","updated":"20230817162004"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Transformation和Action"}]},{"ID":"20230817162005-meyty6q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230817162005-meyty6q","updated":"20230817162005"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"接下来我们详细分析一下Spark中对RDD的操作"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Spark对RDD的操作可以整体分为两类："},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Transformation和Action"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这里的Transformation可以翻译为转换，表示是针对RDD中数据的转换操作，主要会针对已有的RDD创建一个新的RDD：常见的有map、flatMap、filter等等"}]},{"ID":"20230817162006-3ut9qwn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230817162006-3ut9qwn","updated":"20230817162006"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Action可以翻译为执行，表示是触发任务执行的操作，主要对RDD进行最后的操作，比如遍历、reduce、保存到文件等，并且还可以把结果返回给Driver程序"}]},{"ID":"20230817162007-ztbcpsc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230817162007-ztbcpsc","updated":"20230817162007"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不管是Transformation里面的操作还是Action里面的操作，我们一般会把它们称之为算子，例如：map算子、reduce算子"}]},{"ID":"20230817162008-lhq9r9c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230817162008-lhq9r9c","updated":"20230817162008"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"其中Transformation算子有一个特性：lazy"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"lazy特性在这里指的是，如果一个spark任务中只定义了transformation算子，那么即使你执行这个任务，任务中的算子也不会执行。"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"也就是说，transformation是不会触发spark任务的执行，它们只是记录了对RDD所做的操作，不会执行。"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"只有当transformation之后，接着执行了一个action操作，那么所有的transformation才会执行。"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Spark通过lazy这种特性，来进行底层的spark任务执行的优化，避免产生过多中间结果。"}]},{"ID":"20230817162009-hck255v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230817162009-hck255v","updated":"20230817162009"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Action的特性：执行Action操作才会触发一个Spark 任务的运行，从而触发这个Action之前所有的Transformation的执行"}]}]}